{"id":268580,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-原山东省人大代表刘英祥遭遇野蛮拆迁（/","date":"2012-12-16T15:15:33Z","modified":"2012-12-16T15:15:33Z","title":"维权网 | 原山东省人大代表刘英祥遭遇野蛮拆迁（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）古稀老人刘英祥系第六届山东省人大代表，还担任过原济南市历城县副县长。他的房屋位于济南市山大北路</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">63</span><span>号</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>号楼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>单元</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">401</span><span>室。去年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日，济南市政府公布第一号房屋征收决定以来，尤其十八大以后，该地区接二连三发生断电、断气、断通讯、断网络、断有线电视事件，且愈演愈烈。刘英祥向法院提起行政诉讼，委托倪文华代理。这更使拆迁办气急败坏，派遣拆迁流氓肆无忌惮地将一至五楼的楼梯扶手拆走，逼老人家搬迁。老人上下楼提心吊胆，随时都有坠楼的危险，但刘英祥老人坚持维权，将行政诉讼进行到底。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>凌晨</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>分，一伙拆迁暴徒趁刘英祥不在家时，突然闯入宿舍楼，将他家的防盗门撬开，钻进室内，砸碎玻璃门窗，砸烂家具和空调、洗衣机等家电（附图片）。刘英祥老人愤怒地说，在诉讼期间，拆迁流氓还在野蛮拆迁，是藐视法律的体现。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当日，刘英祥向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>警察赶到现场，结果不了了之。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bHwgzMl05Xk/UM3SFd-UQvI/AAAAAAAAW5o/fWp4v__CQLw/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-bHwgzMl05Xk/UM3SFd-UQvI/AAAAAAAAW5o/fWp4v__CQLw/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-bc9C0iWrR1Y/UM3SG0lDTyI/AAAAAAAAW5w/WdNozRJXZaE/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-bc9C0iWrR1Y/UM3SG0lDTyI/AAAAAAAAW5w/WdNozRJXZaE/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"237\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_bla